OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be cloudy with
OL,6,Fshowers, mostly in the south. It will
OL,7,Fbecome drier with bright spells, these
OL,8,Fmainly in the north and the east.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FAny early showers will soon
OL,11,Fclear and cloud will increase from the
OL,12,Fevening as outbreaks of rain push east
OL,13,Fovernight.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FCloudy with rain at first,
OL,16,Fthis soon clearing, becoming mostly
OL,17,Fdry with bright spells and the odd
OL,18,Fafternoon shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
