OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells interspersed with showers
OL,7,FMonday. Cloudy with rain, some heavy,
OL,8,Ffor a time early Tuesday and again
OL,9,Flater Wednesday.
